--JIRA PHP Class--
Two classes taht can be used with the JIRA REST API.

-- class.restrequest.php--
This class will do the following:
	
	-Handle requests to a REST api with verbs of PUT, PUSH, DELETE, POST and GET.

--class.jira.php--
This class will do the following methods:
	
	- Create a new case
	- Update a case
	- Retrive jql issue queries.